# Data Sources and Integrations

- Adapters must implement `MarketplaceAdapter` in `apps/api/src/adapters.ts`.
- All adapter output must map to `CanonicalListing` from `packages/shared/src/index.ts`.
- Normalize external data using `apps/api/src/normalization.ts` helpers.
- Runtime credentials (`runtime_credentials`) override env credentials.
- Never log secrets, tokens, or password-like values.
- Preserve partial search results when a marketplace fails; do not fail the whole search.
- New adapter work requires:
  - mapping tests
  - auth/error path tests
  - compatibility with retry + rate-limit wrappers in `search-pipeline.ts`
- Trust messaging must keep shared disclaimer semantics:
  - maisonDeux aggregates listings
  - maisonDeux does not authenticate items
